'''Obsidian Swordfish''' is a {{Rarity|Mythical}} fish found in the [[Roslit Bay#Roslit Volcano|Volcano]] in [[Roslit Bay]].

== Description ==
{{Description|Swordfish are extremely strong and notable due to their long flattened bill that resembles a sword, as their name implies. This swordfish has adapted to it's magma filled life, and is now imbued with Obsidian skin.|Bestiary Entry}}

